3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：<a href="https://worksinprogress.co/issue/how-dc-densified">艾米丽·汉密尔顿</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>我强烈推荐的另一篇优秀文章是<a href="https://onefinaleffort.com/blog/a-detailed-look-at-minneapolis-housing-supply-reforms">马修·马尔特曼对明尼阿波利斯住房改革的分析</a>。他认为，虽然大肆宣扬的废除单户住宅区划的影响不大，但它是对供应产生重大影响的一揽子改革计划之一。他指出，自这些改革生效以来，明尼阿波利斯的租金相对于附近城市有所下降： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa56fb715-4082-4355-90c0-b0b991e394c0_847x499.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa56fb715-4082-4355-90c0-b0b991e394c0_847x499.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa56fb715-4082-4355-90c0-b0b991e394c0_847x499.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa56fb715-4082-4355-90c0-b0b991e394c0_847x499.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa56fb715-4082-4355-90c0-b0b991e394c0_847x499.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpubl